        "subject": "LU-10026: Page buffer pool for compression",
        "message": "LU-10026: Page buffer pool for compression\n\nAdds a pool of contiguous buffers for compression.\n- Init before Lustre runs\n- Able to access and free the memory buffers by buffer pointer or page-wise\n- One can request a single buffer or a bundle of buffers (\"atomic\" loan)\n\nChange-Id: Ibeb62096fb62ce06e3b00bdbda60b4b72ffcb136\nTest-Parameters: forbuildonly fstype=zfs\nSigned-off-by: Anna Fuchs <anna.fuchs@informatik.uni-hamburg.de>\n"
      },
